Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前如果慊人或父親下令的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.47,0:01:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都要消除記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.97,0:01:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明知這樣會傷害由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是把他的朋友的記憶消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像雪一樣寒冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.72,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人當時所說的話或許是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.99,0:01:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又出去了 到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說小透嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到朋友家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天吃晚飯的時候就說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.01,0:02:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從來不聽別人說話的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆！她很少出門的嘛 都怪她不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透已經很習慣這個家了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾家花兒今在何方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好大哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家果然家大業大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是為了草摩同學他們的秘密而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 或許能見到當家的慊人先生哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.71,0:02:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅…紅葉 危、危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很準時哦 門沒關 進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.29,0:02:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到草摩家！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！裡面也好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.13,0:03:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門裡面好像一個小鎮一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像來到一個未知的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是好安靜哦 好像沒有住人似的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種氣氛讓我更緊張了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊 波鳥住在更裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很怕波鳥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不、不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡他哦 妳應該也會很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拘束 放輕鬆點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種氣氛令我更緊張了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這裡會有女人的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在有點意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去那麼嚴肅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.99,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…他說有很重要的事情要說 莫非是要罵我!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在這麼氣派的豪邸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不想跟住在帳篷裡的我有任何瓜葛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣冒冒失失的 真的是太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透？妳是不是哪裡不舒服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓波鳥看看吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是個醫生哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒、沒關係 我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是醫生 也只不過是草摩家的主治大夫而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且有一半的時間都在照顧慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的專長就是容易生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡拐彎抹角 我們就開門見山的說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道十二生肖秘密的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們家族中也只是少數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.04,0:04:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳這個外人知道這個秘密實在很不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該立即消除妳的記憶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過慊人並沒有下達這項指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,允許妳和他們一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.19,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在紫吳家生活還快樂吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的…很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸妳還是儘早搬出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再和草摩家有任何瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開紫吳的家 回到親戚的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是妳原本的生活吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳那傢伙應該什麼也沒告訴妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.21,0:05:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被怪物附身的草摩家並沒有妳想像的那麼快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.01,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詭異…陰森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還被詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在妳後悔與草摩家有任何關聯之前…搬走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 我想帶小透到庭院裡走走可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.81,0:06:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶妳到我喜歡的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家並沒有妳想像的那麼快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.56,0:06:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詭異…陰森…還被詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很安靜吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家的人今天都為了正月而在內院裡做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正月的時候大家都會聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的節日 忙死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.51,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從大門外林蔭道到本家這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住的人全都是草摩家的人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那不是很多人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.22,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳和由希以前也住在這裡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能住在這裡的人不是像我一樣是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是知道這個秘密的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.90,0:07:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳這個外人知道這個秘密實在很不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.74,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥的左眼幾乎看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.84,0:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥有一個情人叫做佳菜 她是波鳥的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個很好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道波鳥被怪物附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只是若無其事的笑笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還訂下婚約…不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人很生氣 非常生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他反對這椿婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動手使波鳥的眼睛受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.13,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而波鳥並沒有責怪慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是佳菜卻十分自責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.34,0:07:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怪自己害波鳥的眼睛受傷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的自責 使她得了心病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.55,0:07:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥不得已將佳菜的記憶消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不忍心看佳菜變得那麼憔悴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.99,0:08:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是把兩人相愛的時光消掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜離開這裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他並不怪慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我多少能夠了解波鳥的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不希望再看到有人會變得和佳菜一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不希望妳受到和佳菜一樣的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小透？妳在哭嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我害妳哭的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉、真的很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.58,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哭是因為波鳥先生太溫柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.32,0:09:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還為我的事擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在需要這份溫柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是波鳥先生才對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫妳倒杯熱茶 進來裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道會下雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.56,0:09:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.63,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對草摩家的事一無所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳用不著知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是忘掉比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉了嗎？波鳥先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳用不著道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.22,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機會的話 我也會和佳菜見面、聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過僅止於此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能夠了解我的意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天說得太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒、沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…我…還要再回那個家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水！不 海、海水!?還是水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼才好？波鳥先生～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是草摩佳菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始擔任你的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好努力的 請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是同一個家族的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻從來沒有說過話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 波鳥先生人很帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在朋友之中也很受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是妳的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳今天的工作 快點做吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.44,0:11:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！是雪 我就知道會下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問你一個問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪融化之後會變成什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說 當然是水囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對！會變成春天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡春天了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.63,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人只要有了感情就能把別人美化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.70,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 她就是我的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幽暗緊閉的草摩家中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.17,0:12:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠都像被冰冷的雪封住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.35,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就像鮮綠蓬勃的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們愛就像是命中注定的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的夢也開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水！不！海水!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要哪一種？波鳥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我要事先說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把龍的私生子丟到浴缸裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能會害死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不知道該怎麼辦啊 只好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…我終於知道原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想你為什麼不讓我抱你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.06,0:13:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你害怕 不想讓人家知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以和別人保持距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是喜歡的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不用怕 不要拒絕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…能夠遇到你 覺得很開心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能喜歡波鳥是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能留在你身邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流淚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿出生以來第一次有人原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人救我的心情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.03,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像春天的氣息吹得凍結的雪融化一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我淚流不止…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就像在做夢一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.18,0:13:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像凝聚了幾十年的幸福一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！我不准你們結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不准！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥？你怎麼了？波鳥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是妳害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是波鳥看不見的話 全都是妳害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慊人！波鳥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以解開草摩家的詛咒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜 快點把波鳥帶走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法解開詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要妳有什麼用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要妳有什麼用！全都是妳害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.26,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是妳害的！全都是妳害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.47,0:14:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我說什麼、做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是一味的哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後她病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.01,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的隱蔽術這時候應該可以派上用場吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該消除她的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前你不是很乾淨俐落的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.19,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在令她痛苦的是和你的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你的愛情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.49,0:15:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠將她從痛苦之中解救出來的只有你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你最後的功用啊 波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也希望能真正獲得解脫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有相逢就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她求你忘掉她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有相逢…就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是否會對別人造成傷害 也不管對方是否哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.32,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要接到命令就會將別人的記憶消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是萬萬沒想到自己最重要的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的回憶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要由自己下手消除…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是報應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 佳菜 已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳再也不會覺得痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天妳會想找一個能夠給妳幸福的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我只能默默祝福妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.53,0:16:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我不能保護你 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該道歉的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能保護妳的人也是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠與你相逢 我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你 我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生都在不會融化的雪中渡過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們做過的夢永遠不會融化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.24,0:17:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於你的指導 讓我得以成為醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是個菜鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救波鳥先生吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠遇到大家 覺得很幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不想失去和他們的關係…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜小姐應該也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 救救波鳥先生吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊、我沒有看 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以先把你移到房間來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.56,0:18:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你躺在那裡 冒昧地用我的髒大衣蓋住你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.76,0:18:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！然後 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的十二生肖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是啊 很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很令人意外哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你沒事 我也就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個…很抱歉 我擅自…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有好一陣子沒有做夢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這場雪的關係嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我可以問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪融化之後會變成什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.90,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…嗯 這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會變成春天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管現在多麼冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天總是會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪一定會融化的 一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷不冷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也很喜歡充滿食慾的秋天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.23,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去買個熱騰騰的東西吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？熱騰騰的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱茶好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?紫吳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀～找妳好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了一隻迷路的兔子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.34,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉！啊 不是熱茶是果汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳久等了 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.59,0:19:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.56,0:19:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕你會嚇到小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藝術家的第六感嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少來了 你是來看正月的準備的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個雖然常頂嘴卻是好朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.40,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 凡人就是會忌妒天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有問波鳥的生肖呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 你希望四歲時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛哭鬼的可笑模樣在出版界流傳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 我不說就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正一下就被識破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.98,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為這有什麼好丟臉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天讓妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過波鳥不是什麼壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.94,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 他很溫柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛、剛剛莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透？離我太遠妳會迷路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳 詛咒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有我能夠幫上忙的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.84,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 妳只要扮演好自己就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天知道了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也有很多事不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 回來晚了…咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說得好 暖爐桌連鬼都好睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.24,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是把他們叫醒的話有點危險 還是暫時別理他們好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.01,0:21:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不管是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都很珍惜 這樣的心情依舊沒有改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠在這個家生活的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.89,0:21:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會很珍惜 很珍惜…
